      "description": "[[/attack extended]]. Hit: The target has the &amp;Reference[Grappled apply=false] condition (escape DC [[lookup @skills.ath.passive]]) from one of six tentacles, and the target has the &amp;Reference[Poisoned apply=false] condition until the grapple ends.\n\nThe tentacle can be damaged, freeing a creature it has Grappled when destroyed (AC 20, HP 10, Immunity to Poison and Psychic damage). Damaging the tentacle deals no damage to the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster}, and a destroyed tentacle regrows at the start of the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster}'s next turn.",
